\subsection{Detailed Description}
settings class 

Used to store game settings like language and key configuration. Contains methods for loading and saving the settings. On GNU/Linux, settings will be saved to $\sim$/.i-team/settings.txt On Windows, settings will be saved to ./userdata/settings.txt 